      <title>新质量标准引发钢材销售暴跌 中国钢铁市场震荡</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-24/china-steel-market-jolted-as-new-quality-standards-trigger-sales</link>
      <description><![CDATA[由于新的质量标准迫使贸易商减少库存，中国钢铁市场面临动荡时期，这给钢铁价格带来压力，并导致铁矿石价格下跌。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-24/china-steel-market-jolted-as-new-quality-standards-trigger-sales</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 24 Jul 2024 06:22:24 GMT</pubDate>
